messages.message:
something strange is happening with our logic for finding affected Cypress tests for PRs
• for my PR (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/59443), only 1 Cypress test was marked as affected and included in the CI run, even though there should be a lot more
• for Danny’s PR (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/59434), no Cypress tests were marked as affected
@CJ could you look into this tomorrow?
